        "description": "<p>Filter your admin comments that have not received a reply by internal user yet.</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jb9MkPPXB_w?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<p>Ignore pingbacks from the loop. You could define a list with admin usernames that would answer from your team.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the entire <code>dx-unanswered-comments</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Navigate to the Comments section and filter the comments above</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add a bulk action to mark as replied</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Implemented feature, where user can mark a comment as replied and mark as not replied</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix a bug listing all when no actual comments are pending</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Filter comments, hide spam</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enhancement: Add extra hooks</li>\n<li>Add-On: Compatible with premium extension &#8220;Hide Unanswered&#8221;</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enhancement: Hiding pingbacks from the list</li>\n<li>Enhancement: Filter by admin usernames</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial version</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
